      "text": "He that goeth forth and weepeth, bearing seed for sowing, Shall doubtless come again with joy, bringing his sheaves [with him].",
      "versionTitle": "American Standard Version"
    },
    {
      "language": "en",
      "ref": "Psalm 126:6",
      "source_id": "web",
      "source_url": "https://ebible.org/engwebp/PSA126.htm",
